        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         <BR>I guess one of the advantages of being a lowbie is that I can pin down exactly what level my pet is.  At level 16, post-patch, I summoned a white (black?) pet -- level 16.  But I noticed something very strange... Instead of hitting for 20 max, as happened pre-patch for a level 16 pet, my pretty hit for 16 max.  </P><P>So, one of several things...</P><P>1)  They've lowered max damage on pets.<BR>2)  A developer got lazy and added the "feature" by simply making the pet con at the highest possible level without changing the pet's level. :)<BR>3)  They did something bad to their pet code...</P><P>My vote is for #3, but I'm probably missing something.  </P><P>Kalee<BR>17th Level Princess of Evil<BR>The Seventh Hammer</P><P>aka Feodor Dustyoasski<BR>53rd Level Monkey<BR>The Seventh Hammer<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
